'''ESFJ'''(外倾/感觉/情感/判断)是[[迈尔斯·布里格斯性格分类法|迈尔斯·布里格斯性格分类法]]中十六种人格类型之一。<ref name=foundation>{{cite web|url=http://www.myersbriggs.org/my-mbti-personality-type/mbti-basics/the-16-mbti-types.asp|title=Myers-Briggs Foundation: The 16 MBTI Types|accessdate=2011-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090513191631/http://www.myersbriggs.org/my-mbti-personality-type/mbti-basics/the-16-mbti-types.asp|archive-date=2009-05-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 在[[柯尔塞气质类型测试|柯尔塞气质类型测试]]中被称为[[供给者_(角色变异)|供给者]]，属于[[监护人_(气质类型)|监护人]]的四种类型之一，约占人口的9%-13%。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.keirsey.com/handler.aspx?s=keirsey&f=fourtemps&tab=2&c=provider|title=Keirsey.com Portrait of the Provider|accessdate=2011-02-11|archive-date=2010-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101030202432/http://keirsey.com/handler.aspx?s=keirsey&f=fourtemps&tab=2&c=provider|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.capt.org/mbti-assessment/estimated-frequencies.htm|title=CAPT|accessdate=2011-02-11|archive-date=2017-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911215111/https://www.capt.org/mbti-assessment/estimated-frequencies.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

